{"tid":418842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反黑 OCTB","createTime":"2017-09-30T02:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T19:16:35.000Z","uid":27273,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"776e93ed1473bcbc4be4b9cc76d1e8eac4e266f3","tid":418842,"uid":27273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:37:18.000Z","msg":"反黑呢套劇幾好睇，睇得出拍攝幾認真。<br />\n啲主角演員我都幾鐘意，特別係李燦森。<br />\n但唔知點解每次佢講完每一句對白<br />\n我都總會覺得接住落嚟佢講：<br />\n「我呢倫都賺夠啦，我都想俾人賺下！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/103653_892d8da019a3d2742578d18a85b0e0b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F103653_892d8da019a3d2742578d18a85b0e0b0.jpg&h=9ddfdc11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無睇過龍咁威嘅巴絲有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede3a82d787dead41907afefb76f9326af5c576d","tid":418842,"uid":63450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"陳小春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了"},{"pid":"9e3cd6051e4e5df1b0669aeb2fe00e0cdc08e17f","tid":418842,"uid":31137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳小春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了</blockquote><br />\n硬係覺得佢講野咬字唔清晰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3690d752bdc55a3417eab80a5bf126077fa9541","tid":418842,"uid":27273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>陳小春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了</blockquote><br />\n硬係覺得佢講野咬字唔清晰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as